{"tid":2510384,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"碧堤半島路口「快閃綠燈」　住戶出車塞足40分鐘　車龍排上停車場6樓","createTime":"2021-04-30T06:33:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-30T06:54:13.000Z","uid":271829,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"682dc08215e221a5cfe52ce97841ecada88add35","tid":2510384,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T06:33:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/GDYZOXZkuRpRgpORFXB3JhvLSxE=/535x713/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BNHYK6XC2RCF7MSLTW2DL7Z3SU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FGDYZOXZkuRpRgpORFXB3JhvLSxE%3D%2F535x713%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBNHYK6XC2RCF7MSLTW2DL7Z3SU.jpg&h=01bd6ba3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nRic指，他於周一（26日）早上在停車場6樓遇上車龍，塞了近25分鐘，至9時左右才排至地面的交通燈位。讀者提供<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/YQxYwRFs89_0NSXuuVadNMt1skw=/535x300/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PPFH7ALSWZCEFMQM4XW4KRQDIA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FYQxYwRFs89_0NSXuuVadNMt1skw%3D%2F535x300%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPPFH7ALSWZCEFMQM4XW4KRQDIA.jpg&h=00d07b71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n屋苑小路有3條行車線，車輛可經此駛出青山公路深井段往屯門（左一線）或九龍（右兩線）。記者周三（28日）早上在場計時，紅燈（上）和綠燈（下）時間分別是約1分43秒和17秒。<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n由8座大廈組成的碧堤半島共有3,345個單位和2,573個住客車位，車輛由停車場駛出屋苑小路後，經過一組交通燈，便能駛上青山公路深井段往屯門或九龍。住戶Ric向《蘋果》表示，較早前當局在深井天主教小學對出一個行人過路處進行工程，將分段過路處改為直行式過路處，工程於4月初完成。惟上周二（20日），他發覺住戶車輛駛出燈口的綠燈時間大幅減少，以往是30秒左右，但當日一瞬間便轉紅燈；他於本周一（26日）錄得綠燈時間只得12秒。<br />\n<br />\n根據Ric提供的片段，他的座駕在周一於停車場6樓遇上車龍，只能緩慢駛往地面閘口。他指當日早上約8時半出車，塞了近25分鐘，至9時左右才排至交通燈位。他平時駛往位於東涌的公司，車程只需約20分鐘，不禁大嘆：「朝朝返工，喺停車場嘅時間仲多過喺條路！」<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210430/J6YIPNPJJNB5FNKJS6TZYCVI7Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210430%2FJ6YIPNPJJNB5FNKJS6TZYCVI7Q%2F&d=SQXEpmicj55cx%2FeODTqnT5ktsUQkmpJZziL8xq2DbDY%3D&h=1398a540\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210430%2FJ6YIPNPJJNB5FNKJS6TZYCVI7Q%2F&h=3fd7a60e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210430/J6YIPNPJJNB5FNKJS6TZYCVI7Q/</a>"},{"pid":"25af46e61747ba0004cc88d426aea82729dbfa09","tid":2510384,"uid":1900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T06:40:08.000Z","msg":"依個星期係有一日依個十字路口d燈奇奇怪怪咁"},{"pid":"9269bc19198ccd58b3542645a6e74fda253fe032","tid":2510384,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T06:44:09.000Z","msg":"ASTON MARTIN<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2da13401cf7aed746447c7544f93eea35cb19934","tid":2510384,"uid":173404,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T06:47:00.000Z","msg":"咁紅燈停幾耐先?<br />\n你話紅燈都係停10幾秒都可以接受啦<br />\n荔枝角道個紅燈停1分半-1分40秒<br />\n綠燈又係20秒都唔夠, 前面架巴士轉綠岩岩好過完到我就轉返紅燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/bus.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你都咪話唔過癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7aec386789e52d21e80680b3e005e13abf2d084","tid":2510384,"uid":173404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T06:48:30.000Z","msg":"原來個post 講左, 疏<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1d142ce37b3e216639a7b4829c79a96fb4b57a4","tid":2510384,"uid":395358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T06:54:13.000Z","msg":"政府又撚死香港人"}]}